https:\/\/www.esisuisse.ch\/fr<\/a>, qui assure la garantie des d\u00e9p\u00f4ts en Suisse.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Garantie des d\u00e9p\u00f4ts Mes d\u00e9p\u00f4ts sont-ils prot\u00e9g\u00e9s par la garantie des d\u00e9p\u00f4ts esisuisse? Oui, Banque Cramer &amp; Cie SA a l&#8217;obligation, comme toute banque et toute maison de titres en Suisse, de signer l\u2019Autor\u00e9gulation \u00abConvention entre esisuisse et ses membres\u00bb. Les d\u00e9p\u00f4ts des clients sont donc assur\u00e9s jusqu&#8217;\u00e0 un plafond de CHF 100\u2019000 par client. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4076,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_seopress_robots_primary_cat":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[68],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9642"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=9642"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9642\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4076"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9642"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=9642"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=9642"}]